data.description: Well maintained, move-in ready home located in the well sought after community of Lake Carolina features a formal dining room, great room with gas log fire place, kitchen with stainless steel appliances, spacious master suite on main level with double vanity.  The second level features a bonus room with closet that can be used as a 4th bedroom or for entertainment.  Spacious backyard conveys patio space, storage shed and lots of space for outdoor entertainment.   *Seller offering $3000 in closing costs and 12 months Home Warranty!   *Roof replaced in 2014. * HVAC replaced in 2018.  *New privacy fence in 2022.   Close to Ft. Jackson, shopping, dining, entertainment, I-77 and I-20.
